{"id": "art-2522", "label": "Art. 2522", "title": "Art. 2522: Valorificarea bunurilor mobile sechestrate în cursul urmăririi penale", "slug": "art-2522", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1079330217\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2068\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1079330217\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 252<sup>2</sup>:\nValorificarea bunurilor mobile sechestrate în cursul urm&#259;ririi penale </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1804594393\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2067\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1804594393\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, în situa&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 252<sup>1</sup> alin. (2)-(3<sup>1</sup>), dac&#259;\nprocurorul care a instituit sechestrul apreciaz&#259; c&#259; se impune\nvalorificarea bunurilor mobile sechestrate, îl sesizeaz&#259; cu o propunere\nmotivat&#259; de valorificare a bunurilor sechestrate pe judec&#259;torul de\ndrepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1520419309\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2066\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1520419309\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i\nsesizat în condi&#355;iile alin. (1) fixeaz&#259; un termen, care nu poate fi\nmai scurt de 10 zile, la care sunt chemate p&#259;r&#355;ile, precum &#351;i\ncustodele bunurilor, atunci când a fost desemnat unul. Participarea\nprocurorului este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2089553116\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2065\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2089553116\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La termenul fixat, în camer&#259; de consiliu, se aduce\nla cuno&#351;tin&#355;a p&#259;r&#355;ilor &#351;i a custodelui faptul c&#259;\nse inten&#355;ioneaz&#259; valorificarea bunurilor mobile sechestrate &#351;i\nli se pune în vedere c&#259; au dreptul de a face observa&#355;ii sau cereri legate\nde bunurile ce urmeaz&#259; a fi valorificate. Dup&#259; examinarea\nobiec&#355;iilor &#351;i cererilor f&#259;cute de p&#259;r&#355;i sau custode,\njudec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i dispune prin încheiere\nmotivat&#259; asupra valorific&#259;rii bunurilor mobile prev&#259;zute la art.\n252<sup>1</sup> alin. (2)-(3<sup>1</sup>). Lipsa p&#259;r&#355;ilor legal\ncitate nu împiedic&#259; desf&#259;&#351;urarea procedurii.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1340882620\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2064\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1340882620\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Împotriva încheierii judec&#259;torului de drepturi\n&#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i prev&#259;zute la alin. (3) se poate face\ncontesta&#355;ie la judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i de\nla instan&#355;a ierarhic superioar&#259; de c&#259;tre p&#259;r&#355;i,\ncustode, procuror, precum &#351;i de c&#259;tre orice alt&#259; persoan&#259;\ninteresat&#259; în termen de 10 zile.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1082619425\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2063\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1082619425\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Termenul prev&#259;zut la alin. (4) curge de la\ncomunicare pentru procuror, p&#259;r&#355;i sau custode sau de la data când au\nluat la cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259; de încheiere în cazul altor persoane\ninteresate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_71832356\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2062\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_71832356\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)P&#259;r&#355;ile sau custodele pot face\ncontesta&#355;ie numai împotriva încheierii prin care judec&#259;torul de\ndrepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i a dispus valorificarea bunurilor mobile\nsechestrate. Procurorul poate face contesta&#355;ie numai împotriva încheierii\nprin care judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i a respins\npropunerea de valorificare a bunurilor mobile sechestrate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_762321865\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2061\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_762321865\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Contesta&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (4) este\nsuspensiv&#259; de executare. Judecarea cauzei se face de urgen&#355;&#259;\n&#351;i cu prec&#259;dere, iar hot&#259;rârea prin care se\nsolu&#355;ioneaz&#259; contesta&#355;ia este definitiv&#259;.</span></p>"}